<p style="margin-left:0" id="career_information">We always welcome to hear from applicants who are interested in developing their careers with us. We prioritize personnel who are creative, initiative, are able to present themselves well and have the desire to advance and contribute. Applicants must also be able to keep pace with the rapid development of the company and possess an awareness of information management as an important management tool.</p>
<p style="margin-left:0" id="career_submit_application">You may send an <a href="javascript:__optOlApp('')" class="link_white_nochange_hover_orange">online application</a> by mentioning the position that you are applying for, or by choosing one of the positions on offer below.</p>
